# Office ↔ Rewards separation

Read `.agent/knowledge/office-rewards-separation.md` before changing School Office.

- Use only `office*` Firestore collections and types under `src/lib/office/`.
- Never import from or write to rewards roster collections (`students`, `classes`, `teachers`) in office code.
- Homeroom/classroom teachers for grades are `officeTeachers` + `officeStudents.teacherId`, not rewards `teachers`.
- Do not reintroduce rewards roster sync/import into office without an explicit migration design.
